Class LibraryData

java.lang.Object
LibraryData
public class LibraryData
extends java.lang.Object

    • mergeEntries

      private int mergeEntries​(java.util.List<BookEntry> loaded)
      Merge the list of book entries with the entries already loaded. Duplicate entries will be discarded (This requires .equals to be implemented for BookEntry).
      Parameters:
      loaded - list of book entries to be merged with data already loaded
      Returns:
      number of book entries added to the library
